text: Good variety of food and staff walks around to take drink orders. Place is also well ventilated with many ceiling fans. The Mei Xi Yong Tau Foo is our go to stall for yummy ingredients and very good laksa soup base.

We came here to have dinner.The place was well lited.We got soon seated and begin ordering food.But This coffee lady has a damn attitude.When I order drink,we decided to order drinks from the lady walking around.We called the old lady but she just bluntly walked across the table and begin cleaning the tables instead.Like is she blind or something.She like treated like we do not exist.When the food arrive,everything seems great and could not find anything wrong with the food.Ok lah ig;)

Very friendly chi char staff at FuLee.  Western food also very good, freshly prepared dishes. Mahan Nasi Padang serves very authentic food with friendly staff too.  Chye Fan ( chai Png) very yummy dishes daily.  Staff are friendly & helpful. Soon Kee HongKong Roasted Delights has authentic roast pork, char siew & roast duck.
